From: Freebuff-Termux maintainer
Date: Tue May 26 2026
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] Add android to supported OS list

The Termux environment reports process.platform as "android", which
npm rejects when installing freebuff. This patch adds "android" to
the allowed OS list in package.json.

diff --git a/package.json b/package.json
index 5d97e6b..a2f1c5c 100644
--- a/package.json
+++ b/package.json
@@ -5,7 +5,7 @@
   "os": [
     "darwin",
     "linux",
-    "win32"
+    "win32",
+    "android"
   ],
   "cpu": [
     "x64",
